metadata.name: Comp Stomp 2022 Commemorative Token #1/50
metadata.description:
This token was made to commemorate the first Comp Stomp Stomp Studios gallery taking place June 19-22, 2023 at 70 Hester Street, New York, New York.

All recipients of this token played an active role financially or otherwise to help make the event a reality.

From June 19-June 22 Comp Stomp Studios at NFT NYC hosted:  
- 8 Different artist and collector curated galleries  
- 157 Individual artists   
- 500 Unique pieces 

Artwork by: POSTWOOK
